the package produces datasets in the popular LeRobot format open-sourced by HuggingFace. Acknowledge their contributions and also mention that the sim_dataset_gen.dataset_builder is a modified version of the dataset builder in the LeRobot package.

run example:
`python sim_dataset_gen/generate_dataset.py examples/dexterous_dataset_config.py --num_envs 10 --num_episodes 100`